00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,950
My family's situation is quite special.

7
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,180
I appreciate your effort into this case.

8
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:55,440
Mr. Xu, you can rest assured.

9
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,870
We've handled cases involving

