14
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:08,030
Alright, I'll leave everything to you then.

15
00:02:09,630 --> 00:02:10,190
Goodbye.

16
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:12,070
How are you leaving? Let me see you off.

17
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,170
No, no need.

18
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,300
This place is a bit out of the way.

19
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:15,510
I've already called a car.

20
00:02:16,230 --> 00:02:17,240
Alright, let's meet up again sometime.

21
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:17,960
Okay, thank you.

22
